# skills-local/ — per-instance skills

Skills placed here are **local to this memory-system instance**: git-ignored,
never synced to your other instances, but installed and fanned out locally
exactly like a generic skill in `../skills/`.

Drop a skill dir here (`<name>/SKILL.md`, same shape as `../skills/<name>/`) and
run `scripts/link-skills.sh` — it symlinks into the harness alongside the
generic skills. No per-skill `.gitignore` edit is needed: the whole folder is
ignored by one line (`/skills-local/*`, with this `.gitkeep` un-ignored).

Generic (synced) skills → `../skills/`. Local (per-instance) skills → here.
